UID:zQMJeT8CT-8jaYiyE317T
SUMMARY:Artists at the Center: Union Cultural Center
DTSTAMP:20260412T043233Z
DTSTART:20260418T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:Journey that blends together Brfazilian traditions and Afro-Bra
	zilian forms such as Samba\, Orixas dance\, Samba de roda and Capoeira Ang
